@startuml C4-Container
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Container.puml

title English Learning App - Container Diagram

Person(user, "English Learner", "Traditional Chinese speaker learning English vocabulary")

System_Boundary(englishApp, "English Learning App") {
    Container(mobileApp, "Android Mobile App", "Kotlin, Android SDK", "Provides English learning interface with word search and revision features")
    
    ContainerDb(localDB, "Local Database", "Room/SQLite", "Stores vocabulary words, definitions, user progress, and revision stages")
    
    Container(apiLayer, "API Integration Layer", "Retrofit, OkHttp", "Handles communication with external dictionary API")
}

System_Ext(cambridgeAPI, "Cambridge Dictionary API", "External dictionary service providing English-Traditional Chinese translations")

System_Ext(androidOS, "Android Operating System", "Provides platform services, storage, and UI framework")

' Relationships
Rel(user, mobileApp, "Interacts with", "Touch interface")
Rel(mobileApp, localDB, "Reads/Writes", "SQL queries")
Rel(mobileApp, apiLayer, "Uses", "Method calls")
Rel(apiLayer, cambridgeAPI, "Fetches definitions", "HTTPS/REST")
Rel(mobileApp, androidOS, "Uses", "System APIs")

' Layout hints
Lay_D(mobileApp, localDB)
Lay_R(mobileApp, apiLayer)

note right of mobileApp
  **Core Components:**
  - Main Menu (Navigation)
  - Dictionary Search Screen
  - Revision/Practice Screen
  - Word Management System
  
  **Architecture:**
  - MVVM Pattern
  - LiveData for reactive UI
  - Navigation Component
end note

note right of localDB
  **Schema:**
  - Words table
  - Revision stages (0-5)
  - User progress tracking
  - Offline functionality
  
  **Data:**
  - English words
  - Chinese translations
  - Example sentences
  - Stage progression
end note

note right of apiLayer
  **Features:**
  - HTTP client configuration
  - Response parsing (JSON)
  - Error handling
  - Caching strategy
  - Network state management
end note

@enduml
